---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
const lastUpdated = "April 4, 2026";
---

<BaseLayout title="Refund Policy">
  <h1>Refund Policy</h1>
  <p><strong>Last updated:</strong> {lastUpdated}</p>

  <h2>1. Free Application</h2>
  <p>Pingr is currently offered as a free application. There are no charges associated with downloading or using the App.</p>

  <h2>2. Future Paid Features</h2>
  <p>If paid features or subscriptions are introduced in the future, this Refund Policy will be updated to reflect the applicable refund terms before any charges are applied.</p>

  <h2>3. App Store Purchases</h2>
  <p>For any purchases made through the Apple App Store, refunds are processed in accordance with Apple's refund policies. To request a refund for an App Store purchase, visit <a href="https://reportaproblem.apple.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">reportaproblem.apple.com</a>.</p>

  <h2>4. Contact</h2>
  <p>If you have any questions about this Refund Policy, please contact us at <a href="mailto:info@pingrhub.com">info@pingrhub.com</a>.</p>
</BaseLayout>
